{{gherdëina}}[[File:39048 Selva di Val Gardena BZ, Italy - panoramio.jpg|thumb|350px|Ududa de Plan d'inviern.]]'''Plan''' ie na [[Frazion (Talia)|frazion]] dl chemun de [[Sëlva]] te [[Gherdëina]]. La frazion ie t'insom ala valeda da ulache la streda pea su sun i [[jëuf]]es. Te Plan finova la [[ferata de Gherdëina]]. Te la frazion dal n ciamp dala codla.
Cun referimënt a ''Plan'' adrovun per [[ladin]] la preposizion ''te'' y nia ''a''. Ejëmpl: ie vede ncuei domesdi ''te'' Plan.

== Mejes ==
I mejes de Plan ie: Aldian, Calonia, La Bula, Crestan, Ciajea, Martin (Hotel Krone), Caspiër, Sotanives Dessëura, Sotanives, Spedel, Fussel Dessëura, Fussel Dessot, Frëina, Mulin, Costa Dessëura (Matie), Costa Dedora, Costa Dedite, Cësanueva, Frata, Curtinea (Mëune), Fungëia, Stofl, Janon, Plan, Ost de Plan, Curijel, Merch, Blënta (Scizer), Linacia, Nucia<ref>Barbara Lanz, Sonja Mitterer: ''Höfekarte Gröden.'' Museum Gherdëina, Urtijëi 2014, ISBN 978-88-909015-0-8.</ref>.

